{"tid":1333112,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[弱智撚入]官員們的星座研究","createTime":"2019-07-19T14:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T05:19:35.000Z","uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c53ca2ba8a07499bcbe91bca982a19052733265b","tid":1333112,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"大家好，我就係弱撚智既星座撚<br />\n<br />\n頭先係隔離台見到班官既生日<br />\n諗緊佢地星座會唔會有共通點<br />\n<br />\n但唔知出生地點同時間，唔知有冇人會知佢地係咪香港出世<br />\n<br />\n假設777係香港中午12點出世（時間唔準，所以唔好理d數字）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9isY1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9isY1.png&h=a49926dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實齋睇星座，都幾符合佢固執唔聽人講既個性<br />\n<br />\n然後係佢既左右手（又係假設中午12點香港出世）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S69is0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS69is0f.png&h=5307932f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌又係天蠍"},{"pid":"cfbe9cb9b26e64d3e8873aa2ef73863e5fcc49dc","tid":1333112,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"比卡超：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXHjWVt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXHjWVt.png&h=51927b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n值得留意既係佢水星山羊，火星天蠍<br />\n<br />\n聰聰：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3zuzHu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3zuzHu.png&h=5a19a450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又天蠍，重要連水星都天蠍我屌"},{"pid":"71846a4496cdbf0ff2ebf0c2e9b3b876dc8b81ec","tid":1333112,"uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"up mud 9"},{"pid":"772463a1618b6a96fb16f52a2d3bef46f2641876","tid":1333112,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71846a4496cdbf0ff2ebf0c2e9b3b876dc8b81ec","tid":1333112,"uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"up mud 9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:47:01.000Z","msg":"無，純粹想睇下佢地星盤有咩共通之處<br />\n我個人覺得佢地幾個既星盤入面既重要星星（太陽/月亮/水星）都有天蠍"},{"pid":"42d0c68f271ac8ea32acdd8dd261aca79d56afae","tid":1333112,"uid":245126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"月亮天蠍 狠毒"},{"pid":"eede38b8c0dd38f2c7cbc24acc0eae82515b23d5","tid":1333112,"uid":203889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"71846a4496cdbf0ff2ebf0c2e9b3b876dc8b81ec","tid":1333112,"uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"up mud 9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"以777為例，佢成個盤都金牛=超級固執唔聽人講野<br />\n月亮天蠍=記仇<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;月亮落入天蠍是一個比較不好的位置，這讓你的情緒反應過於強烈、執著與深沉，在感情上也是無法容許背叛，佔有慾與掌控慾對你而言&hellip;&rdquo;"},{"pid":"79e4de148554082e0460eeed08ec458f215d80d9","tid":1333112,"uid":33776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"之前都有留意到林鄭係月蠍<br />\n但見到鄭若驊同盧偉聰都係天蠍<br />\n真係嚇左一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79873da646fd3aab8074414d41edbd32d35ccd7a","tid":1333112,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"同場加映<br />\n689<br />\n太陽獅子+水星獅子：唔輸得，要做大佬<br />\n月亮山羊：現實主義，冷血<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfibN61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnfibN61.png&h=e80fc724&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90d8262cf1ddf95174ce0798b4b61c2b37321827","tid":1333112,"uid":409,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"所以佢當初係CCTVB做專訪喊我信佢係真心喊<br />\n條友根本覺得自己係為左香港好所以先推條條例出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942ee94667d9b8690e2a390a2fa7b669c326c06a","tid":1333112,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79e4de148554082e0460eeed08ec458f215d80d9","tid":1333112,"uid":33776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"之前都有留意到林鄭係月蠍<